gomodel:SYNGO_2620  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.2: \"Overexpression of Slitrk1 and Slitrk2 in cultured neurons increases the amount of presynaptic excitatory and inhibitory contacts\". Experimental description: - \"E18-19 rat embryos were obtained from Sprague Dawley females (Charles River). Cultures of hippocampal neurons were prepared from the embryos according to previously described protocols\"\n- \"Full-length human Slitrk1 (aa 1-696) and human Slitrk2 (aa 1-845) ....\"" ;
